Global Healthcare Wipes Market Insights
Healthcare Wipes Market size was valued at USD 2.15 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.73 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Healthcare Wipes Market Overview
The global healthcare wipes market was valued at USD 18.05 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 7.7% from 2025 to 2030. This growth is driven by heightened awareness of hygiene and infection control, especially following the COVID-19 pandemic. Healthcare wipes are essential for patient care, surface disinfection, and sanitization of medical equipment, playing a crucial role in infection prevention strategies. The increasing prevalence of chronic diseases and an aging population requiring frequent healthcare services further contribute to the market's expansion. Technological advancements, such as the development of environmentally friendly and more effective wipes, also support market growth.

